comment:
Drammers club online pour. Amazing stuff, among the best of the night and it also included masters collection seasoned oak and the woodford baccarat bottle finished in cognac casks. 

Nose: Maple Syrup, Caramel, Chocolate, Cinnamon, Oak, Cherry, Apple, Pineapple, Banana Bread, Cloves, Spearmint, Dill, Soil, Nutmeg, Nougat, Peach

Palate: Maple Syrup, Caramel, Pepper, Cinnamon, Banana Bread, Citrus, Cherry, Chocolate, Raisins, Cloves, Tree Bark 

Finish: Maple Syrup, Cinnamon, Pepper, Caramel, Walnuts, Cherry, Vanilla, Chocolate
Oak, vanilla,  cherries....oh my so good!
